# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GNOS RAG Bot - Environment Configuration Template
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys
# cp .env.template .env

# ── GOOGLE GEMINI API KEYS (Primary Provider) ─────────────────────
# Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikeys
# Free: 1M tokens/day per key
# 
GEMINI_API_KEY_1=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_1_HERE
GEMINI_API_KEY_2=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_2_HERE

# ── GROQ API KEYS (Fallback Provider) ──────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://console.groq.com
# Free: 100k tokens/day per key
# 
GROQ_API_KEY_1=YOUR_GROQ_API_KEY_1_HERE
GROQ_API_KEY_2=YOUR_GROQ_API_KEY_2_HERE
GROQ_API_KEY_3=YOUR_GROQ_API_KEY_3_HERE

# ── HUGGINGFACE TOKEN (Optional) ────────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# Only needed if using HF models/datasets
#
HF_TOKEN=YOUR_HUGGINGFACE_TOKEN_HERE

# ── SERVER CONFIGURATION ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Port for local development (Render uses $PORT env var)
#
PORT=8000

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES:
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# HuggingFace Spaces:
#   1. Create a HF Space (Python + FastAPI)
#   2. Upload this repo
#   3. Set these env vars in Space settings
#   4. Space auto-deploys to: https://username-gnos-rag-bot.hf.space/
#
# Render.com:
#   1. Connect GitHub repo
#   2. Set env vars in Dashboard
#   3. Start Command: uvicorn api:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
#   4. Deploys to: https://gnos-rag-bot.onrender.com/
#
# Local Development:
#   1. Create .env file with your keys
#   2. Run: python -m uvicorn api:app --reload
#   3. Test at: http://localhost:8000/health
#   4. API endpoint: POST http://localhost:8000/ask
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
